Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.63,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your ball sack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.76,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.10,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gi-Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They got stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to ride out \Nthe storm on this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.20,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to \Nweather the stormy seas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.97,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,with that heavy anchor \Ndangling from our boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.09,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We should apologize before \Nthey figure out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:45.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,For getting tangled up in \Ntheir old man's ball sack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and treating him like a ball sack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, we'll be murdered \Nby the family of demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He'll make it work somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:02.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for our success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:03.64,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:07.09,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just spit out \Ncliches and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.80,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about Kondo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:12.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's his own fault for getting \Ntangled in the ball sack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.65,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.79,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget your shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.95,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I can lend you my Temote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I prefer Tsubakiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.19,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I go for Vidal Hahhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:27.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think I stayed in the bath \Ntoo long, so I'd like to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.32,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,What? You haven't washed your body yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.65,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be considerate \Nand give our family some space?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.22,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:41.47,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,We were the ones who barged in \Non the bath you had reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.64,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow us to wash your backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.48,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot leave before I've \Nshown my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to show his appreciation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.98,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,He won't let us leave \Nuntil he's gotten revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.49,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.99,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.87,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to wash their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.91,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can wash ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.10,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.76,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,When someone stands behind me, \NI get the urge to beat him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.59,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop making threats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.88,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to let \Nyour sadistic side take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.15,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let them wash your backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of \Nyou, Grandpa Ball-Sack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:24.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla is killing \Nour chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.39,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash Dad's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.80,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if there are \Nany spots that itch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.24,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:34.15,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,When you were little, you \Nused to wash my back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.20,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,You would always get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.20,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,You would yell at me to wash harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.91,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.31,Main01,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,His skin has peeled off, Brother Hedoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.23,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.95,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Dad used a sponge with \Nnails to wash himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.88,Main01,Saburo,0000,0000,0000,,When did he become so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.42,Main01,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this isn't Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-It must be, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The soap. He must be \Nallergic to the soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.99,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Would he start gushing blood \Nbecause he's allergic to the soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The soap on Earth is really acidic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.19,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so you have to be careful \Nor your body will dissolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.86,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.44,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-It must be hard when you don't \Nknow anything about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach you the Earth \Nway of taking a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so please have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.96,Main01,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Earthlings are so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:29.15,Main01,Goro,0000,0000,0000,,They allowed us in the bath that \Nthey had previously reserved,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.46,Main01,Goro,0000,0000,0000,,and they're even offering \Nto wash our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.87,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.53,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, we just want you to \Nenjoy your stay on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.66,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are we doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It beats having the skin \Nripped off our backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.64,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Washing their backs \Nis just as dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.74,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But we can prevent any further damage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.48,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to Kondo-san by teaching \Nthem how we clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:59.17,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Let us learn how they wash \Ntheir bodies in Edo, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.05,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.84,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be really delicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.99,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,'cause Kondo-san's body can't take much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Hedoro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,First, you must have a gentle mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The soap on Earth is strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so the softest of sponges \Ncan still hurt your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,First, we add lotion to the \Nwater to make it smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.51,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of bath are we talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.38,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to teach them how to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.38,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,wash at the bathhouses you frequent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't frequent them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If the water is slimy enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.52,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody will notice when \Nthere's an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.19,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.52,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Your mind is a pile of slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.02,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a fan, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.03,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,And he already slimed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.53,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, he's smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.55,Main01,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,My body is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.03,Main01,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.63,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They're all in pain, Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.23,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.82,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like their weakness is lotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:57.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Their weakness is lotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, most guys have a weakness for lotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:07.18,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Lotion is getting in my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.05,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Odd Jobs. Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This liquid kills germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The pain means that the germs are dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:18.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we should probably wash it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.11,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pour water on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wash off the lotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.16,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who poured lotion \Nall over the floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.49,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.42,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, am I doing it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.12,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to copy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san, we have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:41.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Act like this is how we bathe in Edo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:43.23,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.93,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you'll end up like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:48.51,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs, are you sure this is \Nthe proper way to apply water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.52,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:53.14,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we bathe in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.84,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,You Edo folk are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:59.25,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,You torture yourselves \Nwhen you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:13:59.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a form of training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.84,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very impressed by you samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.87,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to \Nstand this treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's running out of patience?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.34,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Any more and he'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:18.62,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust this guy with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.09,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.13,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make up for all \Nthe previous failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:26.86,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,First, we pull the head out of the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.56,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and wash it with lukewarm wate-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.54,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wate-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.14,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,H-He won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.54,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wate-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.65,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,But you're actually trying to \Nimpale your forehead on the horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.15,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Even Hijikata-san screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.72,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.51,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we make amends \Nfor the previous step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.16,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:59.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've never heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:14:59.97,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how we bathe in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.38,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard is ignoring my mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.65,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.68,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saving your \Nass this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.49,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, think long and hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.76,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You've done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.61,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty disgusting to try to pass \Noff your mistake as an Edo tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.50,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Then what the hell have you \Nbeen doing this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.69,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.01,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.69,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,He's figured out that something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.89,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't follow this practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:34.20,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody in the Shinsengumi does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.47,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Sogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.20,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You're helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.56,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.71,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,You aim for the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.83,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.33,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.25,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why he \Nwould jump to my rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.67,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see why!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.28,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.35,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Do these people even realize \Nthat we're in a bathhouse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do \Nwith bathing anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And why are the Hedoro brothers \Nletting you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:08.28,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I see, there are many \Ndifferent practices in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.63,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san! Kondo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.06,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a barbaric practice that was \Nintroduced by some country bumpkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.85,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to follow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.36,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:22.90,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Since the practice would \Ndamage our precious horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.46,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:30.14,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for the Dakini, our horns are \Nalmost as important as our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.23,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,One represents our pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.97,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,The other represents our soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.97,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,If our horns are damaged, our \Npride and soul are tarnished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of a Dakini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.48,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,...is stuck in the dirtiest \Nplace in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it out before they notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.06,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It's completely stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.95,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san's rectal \Nmuscles are superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.24,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.12,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you snap them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:00.87,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Saburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.37,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Your horns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with his horns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.08,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Saburo's horns appear to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.13,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.24,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.43,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I could have sworn that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I-It must have been your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.76,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You stuck them in upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.64,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You stabbed them right into his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.39,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it was tough \Ngetting those horns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.89,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I snapped Shiro's horns off \Nand stuck them on Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.04,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't help anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.96,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Now Shiro's missing his horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.32,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to snap off \NGoro's horns next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.40,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Will it ever end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll take one horn each from \NGoro and Jiro to stick on Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.06,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.02,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You're just making it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:38.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What about the sixth one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.01,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a sixth brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.37,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We only have five to work with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.65,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saburo, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.72,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.92,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,If you fool around too much, \Nyour precious horns will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.92,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro! Your horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with his horns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.97,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Now he docked them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.43,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shiro's horns appear to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.33,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.45,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's two of them, so \Nthere should be four horns...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.33,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:03.71,Main01,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,There are four horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.43,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Those are completely different horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.09,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.62,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.96,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,How can he believe this crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Such strong horns...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.59,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,wrong with the horns that \Nare stuck in his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to wash your backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.45,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too scared to go near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.70,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kiddy Bath\NDo not jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.84,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to throw them in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.70,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.14,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you wash someone's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.71,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you dispose of a body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.76,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.99,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's ball sack has surfaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:38.72,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.01,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a ball sack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.72,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That means you've \Nreturned to your former self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:48.98,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you enjoy your stay on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.73,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.59,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.73,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It was a terrible experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn, he's pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.42,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.21,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We were calling him a ball sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:01.76,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:02.74,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.93,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm very sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.75,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't like Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:15.50,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here so you could \Nshow the family the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:20.63,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see if you were \Nliving a proper life in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:25.10,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,When you were little, you \Nspent your days alone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:29.02,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,because your appearance \Nscared everyone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:34.52,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to see that you weren't \Nalone on this distant planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.28,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It was a terrible experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.44,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad impression of Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:43.53,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:47.40,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Because I met some friendly \Npeople who tried their best
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.04,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,to make me welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.05,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hedoro, you've found some good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:03.84,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.21,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to be \Nfriends with our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.06,Main01,Chibi,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.90,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:17.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we misunderstood \Ntheir intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,A scary family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.58,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say they're a pretty nice family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:32.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make ourselves scarce then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.84,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.58,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.44,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.60,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:47.10,Main01,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show our appreciation \Nin an Edo fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.93,Main01,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:52.52,Main01,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do for them everything \Nthey've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.02,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:01.66,Main01,Hedoro,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn to wash \Nyour backs Edo-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.53,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.53,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,When I said we should leave together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.54,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I was always the one who had to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:16.38,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Until my wet hair dried,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:21.57,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,and my soap became hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:26.12,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You would embrace me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.75,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,and say that it was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:29.51,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:21.70,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.35,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing that you will \Nbe the star next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:28.14,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I became as excited as a ****** ** ****!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:28.95,Main01,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.06,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.85,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Jugem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:30.80,Main01,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:31.73,Main01,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Jugem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.50,Main01,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't understand the title,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:34.85,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you should do some research.
